<br>
Also, some people might hate soloing, but I really don't find anything wrong with it, grouping is just as boring as soloing for me, raids are the only really fun things, once agian, for me.  I don't know about other servers, but wizards are greatly needed, usually REQUIRED on Xegony raids.  A druid isn't going to run back to some location in ToV to port the last person out.  Its true that our main purpose these days is teleportation, but its a purpose!  Everyone has to have theirs.<br>
<br>
Well, I think thats enough ranting for today.  Just relax and don't worry - after all, it is a game.<br>
